author: TurtLes_BrickBuilds
title: Amazing set..!
review:
I was wondering around the Lego store in Disneyland paris 27/9/18 and I came across this in the store.i absolutely love the movie so I thought *I need that set* so I brought it. Came back home and started to build..! It's a great set I highly recommend..! I am very happy as well to say I was one of the 1st people to get this set.. It came out for the public in october but because I was at Disney they got them in early..!

10/10 experience building..
